# US Water Grade - Redirect www to non-www (HTTPS only, HTTP is auto-upgraded by Cloudflare)
https://www.uswatergrade.com/* https://uswatergrade.com/:splat 301!

# CalorieData - Redirect www to non-www (if needed)
https://www.caloriedata.org/* https://caloriedata.org/:splat 301!

# CalorieData - Force HTTP to HTTPS (Google indexed some HTTP URLs)
http://caloriedata.org/* https://caloriedata.org/:splat 301!

# Fix 404 compare pages with invalid food slugs
/compare/ruffles-potato-chips-vs-trail-mix /compare/potato-chips-vs-trail-mix/ 301
/compare/ruffles-potato-chips-vs-trail-mix/ /compare/potato-chips-vs-trail-mix/ 301
/compare/amaranth-vs-starbucks-via-latte-speciality-coffee-beverage-caramel-caramel /compare/ 301
/compare/amaranth-vs-starbucks-via-latte-speciality-coffee-beverage-caramel-caramel/ /compare/ 301

